pos_examples: Now, apply the action "turn_to" to satellite yew, direction screen and direction bastion.
Once you are done, please apply the action "switch_off" to instrument star_213 and satellite dress_red.

First, apply the action "take_image" to satellite roof_11, direction rain, instrument teddy and mode kumquat_8 and then apply the action "calibrate" to satellite kumquat, instrument frame_9 and direction object_50.

(take_image roof_11 rain teddy kumquat_8)
(calibrate kumquat frame_9 object_50)
The next step is to apply the action "switch_on" to instrument object_260 and satellite roof_11.
